{"tid":1015571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北極熊大量入侵！俄島嶼居民嚇到足不出戶","createTime":"2019-02-10T06:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T08:25:12.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"13fa366ac25ca73d0c11a5867b18615bbb00afc5","tid":1015571,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯新地島（Novaya Zemlya）當局宣布進入緊急狀況，共52隻北極熊出現在該區的人類屯墾區域。北極熊因為氣候變遷，被迫登陸尋找食物。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n新地島官員表示，新地島有數千名人口，當地已出現北極熊攻擊人類，並進入住宅和公共建築的案例。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n俄羅斯將北極熊列為瀕臨絕種動物，禁止獵殺北極熊。俄國聯邦環境局也拒絕發布射殺許可證。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n官員表示，這些北極熊漸漸不怕巡警和警告訊號，這代表當局需要採取更激烈的措施。如果嚇唬北極熊的方法不奏效，選擇性射殺恐成唯一解套辦法。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n新地島主要居住區白鯨灣（Belushya Guba）當局表示，附近共有52隻北極熊，有6-10隻一直待在白鯨灣轄區內。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n當地行政主管穆辛（Vigansha Musin）表示：「我從1983年就在新地島，過去從未有如此多的北極熊大量入侵。」<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n平民生活備受威脅與干擾，部分民眾不敢離家，家長也不願孩童去上學。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n北極海的海冰因氣候變遷消融，北極熊被迫改變狩獵習慣，花更多時間在陸地找食物，結果可能更容易與人類發生衝突。"},{"pid":"7bce82e0837404042b6888bbf327f64b6b981767","tid":1015571,"uid":28155,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T06:34:05.000Z","msg":"這些北極熊漸漸不怕巡警和警告訊號，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bd335875192e2d37e5b63c08ffc81b1a73246d","tid":1015571,"uid":30067,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:37:21.000Z","msg":"因天氣問題俾人迫走 又要俾人殺"},{"pid":"f2e07466366028e451d628ec1b6b089e2ee32d1a","tid":1015571,"uid":82028,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7bce82e0837404042b6888bbf327f64b6b981767","tid":1015571,"uid":28155,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T06:34:05.000Z","msg":"這些北極熊漸漸不怕巡警和警告訊號，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:38:52.000Z","msg":"派乜膠 你以為佢地警告係舉旗叫佢地走？"},{"pid":"c9fd280ff2fc0fd6018b5611c550248c5f5dfdcd","tid":1015571,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"環保L/動保L : 只係人類入侵北極熊活動範圍<br />\n希望人熊共處"},{"pid":"ee6c25f10429cead79d8a29ed23f18909db6ce1a","tid":1015571,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"射支沙皇過去咪搞掂"},{"pid":"ea71535e0909fcedcd6198835fcf33aa807e0e9b","tid":1015571,"uid":54126,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:44:22.000Z","msg":"人類破壞環境<br />\n動物被迫遷徙但又有俾人射殺之險<br />\n動物無立足之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d71572288979e24427136d366bd54c706d030c","tid":1015571,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:47:32.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族都會驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609e2ba252f0eaa628df39519580f0252073fe07","tid":1015571,"uid":73443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:47:55.000Z","msg":"起返個保育區係咪咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b30149a2b1d914355c8c40f3844126d0b4abc6","tid":1015571,"uid":92042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:53:53.000Z","msg":"比返間屋隻熊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088b4f19762dec9376a270b4943321c6f037f428","tid":1015571,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:22:39.000Z","msg":"引入中國人"},{"pid":"b1e0abaa4158b265ceca294df06